data.description: Charming on Isabella Street! Beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home is move-in ready and waiting for a new owner! The home offers over 2400 sq ft and features an open floor plan kitchen and den, large livingroom with fireplace, and formal livingroom. There is so much character in this home. Beautiful hardwood floors throughout, built-in shelving, pocket doors, 9' ceilings (some with tongue and groove pine), and original moldings around the fireplace. The kitchen offers newer stainless appliances, lots of cabinetry, a tiled backsplash, 2 pantry closets, recessed lighting, and a breakfast bar. Bedrooms are all nicely sized with ample closet space. Shared hall bathroom with updated tub/shower and primary bathroom has an updated walk-in shower. Addition closets close to bedrooms and a large attic. Massive utility room off of kitchen with exterior door to carport, can double as a mudroom, craft room/office space, and has am attached half bath. Updated panel box and double pane windows. Built in 1950 but has been lovingly cared for! Low maintenance brick exterior has been recently painted and new custom shutters have been added. Covered patio with new SunShade overlooks a fully fenced backyard. On a corner lot in town, yet it seems private. Wired building in the back yard offers more storage. Minutes from everything in town! City utilities, and high-speed internet available. Convenient to Albany, Tifton, Cordele, and Moultrie. Call for more information or to schedule a tour!
